    <data key="d0">ZS Associates: Building a SelfService Enterprise Data Engineering Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JG5p-i8Cr2E</data>
    <data key="d2">Millions of API requests every month and 100s of data access requests per month. Platform services are running on EKS and the application logic in EMR. Data governance automation reduced the time to market. Reduction in time for building data engineering pipelines by 30-40%. Cost controlling using auto scaling capabilities.</data>
